<p><span>来源：<span>中新网</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-08-22 20:03</p>
<p><i><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200822/45bd567030504ebd9ad3d1f81cf8df38.jpeg" /></i></p>
